{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":3000,"text":"Two years ago, I stood on the TED stage in Arusha, Tanzania."},{"time":7000,"text":"I spoke very briefly about one of my proudest creations."},{"time":12000,"text":"It was a simple machine that changed my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":16000,"text":"Before that time,"},{"time":18000,"text":"I had never been away from my home"},{"time":21000,"text":"in Malawi."},{"time":24000,"text":"I had never used a computer."},{"time":26000,"text":"I had never seen an Internet."},{"time":30000,"text":"On the stage that day, I was so nervous."},{"time":35000,"text":"My English lost,"},{"time":39000,"text":"I wanted to vomit."},{"time":41000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":45000,"text":"I had never been surrounded by so many azungu,"},{"time":49000,"text":"white people."},{"time":51000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":54000,"text":"There was a story I wouldn't tell you then."},{"time":57000,"text":"But well, I'm feeling good right now."},{"time":60000,"text":"I would like to share that story today."},{"time":63000,"text":"We have seven children in my family."},{"time":65000,"text":"All sisters, excepting me."},{"time":69000,"text":"This is me with my dad when I was a little boy."},{"time":74000,"text":"Before I discovered the wonders of science,"},{"time":77000,"text":"I was just a simple farmer"},{"time":79000,"text":"in a country of poor farmers."},{"time":82000,"text":"Like everyone else, we grew maize."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86000,"text":"One year our fortune turned very bad."},{"time":91000,"text":"In 2001 we experienced an awful famine."},{"time":96000,"text":"Within five months all Malawians began to starve to death."},{"time":103000,"text":"My family ate one meal per day, at night."},{"time":107000,"text":"Only three swallows of nsima for each one of us."},{"time":111000,"text":"The food passes through our bodies."},{"time":113000,"text":"We drop down to nothing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117000,"text":"In Malawi, the secondary school,"},{"time":120000,"text":"you have to pay school fees."},{"time":122000,"text":"Because of the hunger, I was forced to drop out of school."},{"time":128000,"text":"I looked at my father"},{"time":130000,"text":"and looked at those dry fields."},{"time":132000,"text":"It was the future I couldn't accept."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136000,"text":"I felt very happy to be at the secondary school,"},{"time":140000,"text":"so I was determined to do anything possible"},{"time":145000,"text":"to receive education."},{"time":147000,"text":"So I went to a library."},{"time":149000,"text":"I read books, science books, especially physics."},{"time":153000,"text":"I couldn't read English that well."},{"time":155000,"text":"I used diagrams and pictures"},{"time":158000,"text":"to learn the words around them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163000,"text":"Another book put that knowledge in my hands."},{"time":167000,"text":"It said a windmill could pump water and generate electricity."},{"time":173000,"text":"Pump water meant irrigation,"},{"time":176000,"text":"a defense against hunger,"},{"time":178000,"text":"which we were experiencing by that time."},{"time":182000,"text":"So I decided I would build one windmill for myself."},{"time":186000,"text":"But I didn't have materials to use,"},{"time":189000,"text":"so I went to a scrap yard"},{"time":191000,"text":"where I found my materials."},{"time":194000,"text":"Many people, including my mother,"},{"time":198000,"text":"said I was crazy."},{"time":200000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":202000,"text":"I found a tractor fan,"},{"time":204000,"text":"shock absorber, PVC pipes."},{"time":206000,"text":"Using a bicycle frame"},{"time":209000,"text":"and an old bicycle dynamo,"},{"time":213000,"text":"I built my machine."},{"time":215000,"text":"It was one light at first."},{"time":218000,"text":"And then four lights,"},{"time":221000,"text":"with switches, and even a circuit breaker,"},{"time":226000,"text":"modeled after an electric bell."},{"time":230000,"text":"Another machine pumps water"},{"time":234000,"text":"for irrigation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237000,"text":"Queues of people start lining up at my house"},{"time":240000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":242000,"text":"to charge their mobile phone."},{"time":244000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":248000,"text":"I could not get rid of them."},{"time":250000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":252000,"text":"And the reporters came too,"},{"time":255000,"text":"which lead to bloggers"},{"time":257000,"text":"and which lead to a call from something called TED."},{"time":262000,"text":"I had never seen an airplane before."},{"time":264000,"text":"I had never slept in a hotel."},{"time":267000,"text":"So, on stage that day in Arusha,"},{"time":271000,"text":"my English lost,"},{"time":274000,"text":"I said something like,"},{"time":277000,"text":"\"I tried. And I made it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":281000,"text":"So I would like to say something"},{"time":283000,"text":"to all the people out there like me"},{"time":286000,"text":"to the Africans, and the poor"},{"time":289000,"text":"who are struggling with your dreams."},{"time":293000,"text":"God bless."},{"time":295000,"text":"Maybe one day you will watch this on the Internet."},{"time":299000,"text":"I say to you, trust yourself and believe."},{"time":304000,"text":"Whatever happens, don't give up."},{"time":306000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":308000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}